@startuml
!include theme.iuml
title DDD Context Map and Integration Contracts
left to right direction
[Identity] as I
[Catalog] as C
[Waiting Room] as W
[Reservation] as R
[Billing] as B
[Ticketing] as T
[Notification] as N
[Analytics] as A
I --> C : Customer/Supplier\nUserId + roles
C --> R : Published Language\nEventSnapshot, VenueLayout, Price
W --> R : Conformist\nAdmissionToken contract
R --> B : Customer/Supplier\nReservationReadyForPayment
B --> T : Partnership\nPaymentSucceeded
R ..> N : Domain event\nreservation.*
B ..> N : Domain event\npayment.*
T ..> N : Domain event\nticket.*
R ..> A : Domain event
B ..> A : Domain event
note bottom of R
  Availability belongs to Reservation, not Catalog.
  Catalog may display an eventually consistent projection;
  Reservation remains authoritative for allocation.
end note
@enduml
